Lizzo,
I can not thank you enough!! This song has been my anthem and reminder of my worth, since I first heard it, right after I found out my husband had been cheating on me for 3 yrs, and him telling me he didn't love me and was in love with his Swamp Whore.

You literally gave me the strength to say no more!! I will no longer be a door mat. I will not let you treat me like this. I am worth more!!

This video just added to why I love this song. I put a smile on my face!!

I can't thank you enough.
